OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,F"There's been iron making on this site
OL,7,Fsince monastic times and there's
OL,8,Falways been change."
OL,10,FSteelmaker Graham Rowland's life, and
OL,11,FTata's plant at Port Talbot, are about
OL,12,Fto undergo unprecedented change as the
OL,13,Ffirst of the two mighty blast furnaces
OL,14,Fare switched off.
OL,16,FIt's the beginning of the end of
OL,17,Fprimary steel making in the UK.
