OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FHe says while he feels privileged to
OL,7,Fhave spent his whole working life
OL,8,Fhere, he will be sorry to go in these
OL,9,Fcircumstances.
OL,11,FGraham will be made redundant as
OL,12,Faround 1900 people are expected to
OL,13,Flose their jobs at the site in Port
OL,14,FTalbot. There are 2500 job losses
OL,15,Fpredicted in total across the UK over
OL,16,Fthe next 12 months, followed by
OL,17,Fanother 300 in the next three years.
OL,19,FAs this blast furnace era draws to a
OL,20,Fclose, another will begin with the
OL,21,Fswitch to an electric arc furnace.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
