OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FIt's a fundamental shift in technology
OL,7,Ffrom virgin steelmaking, to producing
OL,8,Fsteel from recycled metal.
OL,10,FTata says it is greener, it will cut
OL,11,Femissions and it is the future.
OL,13,FBut now is a time for reflection.
OL,15,FWhen Graham started work, there were
OL,16,F18,000 workers in this plant. He says
OL,17,Fnumbers have been dropping ever since.
OL,19,FPutting on a brave face, he says:
OL,20,F"That's progression and you just have
OL,21,Fto accept it."
