OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FNot everyone has accepted the speed of
OL,7,Fthe transition here.
OL,9,FThe unions put forward a proposal for
OL,10,Fa slower transition. They argued to
OL,11,Fkeep one blast furnace open - number
OL,12,F4, which still has nine years of life
OL,13,Fin it - while a new arc is built.
OL,15,FIt would have given the workforce, and
OL,16,Fthe community which depends on the
OL,17,Fplant, a chance to catch their breath
OL,18,Fand retrain.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
