OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FIt would also have avoided thousands
OL,7,Fof workers entering the local job
OL,8,Fmarket all at the same time.
OL,10,FHowever, as our guide from Tata for
OL,11,Fthe day explained, it is logistically
OL,12,Fimpossible to keep one blast running
OL,13,Fand build an arc furnace at the same
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,16,FHe said it would take twice as long,
OL,17,Fcost twice as much and the company has
OL,18,Fruled it out.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
