OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FWe head from the high-tech control
OL,7,Froom, with cameras trained on blast
OL,8,Ffurnaces 4 and 5, to the iron-making
OL,9,Fplant.
OL,11,FVisually, it's basic and spectacular
OL,12,Flike the best bonfire night fireworks
OL,13,FI've ever seen spewing out of a
OL,14,Fglowing cave.
OL,16,FWe watch Blast Furnace No. 5 being
OL,17,F"tapped off". It's a highly controlled
OL,18,Fand regulated environment but it looks
OL,19,Fincredible.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
