OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FIt is like a vision of Dante's
OL,7,FInferno, but perhaps the best
OL,8,Fdescription is from the workers
OL,9,Fthemselves, who refer to this part of
OL,10,Fthe plant as the Eye of Sauron from
OL,11,FLord Of The Rings.
OL,13,FWe see the area where the new electric
OL,14,Farc furnace will be built in a
OL,15,F#1.25billion investment over the next
OL,16,Fthree years.
OL,18,FThe company is keen to emphasise that
OL,19,Fsomething radical had to be done.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
