OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FTata says this plant has been losing a
OL,7,Fmillion pounds a day for years and the
OL,8,Farc will guarantee a future for steel
OL,9,Fhere - just a different one.
OL,11,FSteelmaking is not ending, it's just
OL,12,Fchanging.
OL,14,FIf your job, or even your identity, is
OL,15,Fthe price of that change, though, it
OL,16,Fcan be very hard to accept, especially
OL,17,Ffor younger workers with families and
OL,18,Fmortgages, or older workers who
OL,19,Fhaven't known anything else.
OL,21,FI ask Graham how he will move on.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
