OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FA new chapter now awaits him, this
OL,7,Fplant and this town built on steel.
OL,8,FThere's sadness and uncertainty here,
OL,9,Fbut also some hope of what's yet to
OL,10,Fcome.
